| Setting                                        | Keep it?     | Reason                            |
| ---------------------------------------------- | -----------  | --------------------------------- |
| `python.defaultInterpreterPath`                | ✅           | Locks interpreter to project venv |
| `python.terminal.activateEnvironment`          | ✅           | Auto-activates venv in terminal   |
| `python.terminal.activateEnvInCurrentTerminal` | ✅           | Keeps terminals isolated          |
| `python.testing.pytestEnabled / pytestArgs`    | ✅           | Enables local testing             |
| `python.analysis.extraPaths`                   | ⚙️ Optional  | Helps IntelliSense                |
| `python.analysis.typeCheckingMode`             | ⚙️ Optional  | Adds mild linting                 |




